snippet.title: 1434 Mahoujin Guru Guru 魔法陣グルグル SNES 1440p 60fps
snippet.description:
Runplays are like movies, they're intended to show you all levels, dialogs and music, they don't show my skill. I upload games every day. 
channel link: https://www.youtube.com/c/RunplaysinHD

Pros:
- Usually much shorter than an ordinary longplay. I skip only boring side quests,
which don't affect the story. I don' t collect every thingamabob and don't search every crook and nanny.
- In speedruns they skip levels, dialogs, cutscenes. And a longplay's usually too long. My runplays are faster than longplays, but with all levels, important dialogs, music and cutscenes, apart from the above
- Cheats used for faster gameplay
- High quality video and audio, don't forget to use 1080p60 mode for better picture
- If available, I play on Hard difficulty for best ending
- I play games every day
